Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.024 --> 00:00:02.132
Pixels make up the data of a photo.

00:00:02.132 --> 00:00:07.055
Every color imaginable can be represented with a combination of red,

00:00:07.055 --> 00:00:08.970
green and blue.

00:00:08.970 --> 00:00:12.490
If you're like me, before you knew it was a bad thing,

00:00:12.490 --> 00:00:17.400
you sat way too close to the TV screen while watching Saturday morning cartoons.

00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:17.900
Sitting so

00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:23.430
close, you could see the red, green and blue bands that made up a color.

00:00:23.430 --> 00:00:26.720
Depending on the type of image you're storing in the computer,

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:32.070
you might also have an additional alpha channel that stores how solid or

